Healthcare providers showcase community outreach photos, while representatives from nonprofits emphasize mission-driven career paths. A robotics startup draws attention by flying a small drone above its booth, and workshops on networking etiquette begin in the adjoining classroom. The dean also stops by to thank recruiters for supporting the university.

A welcome announcement outlining the fair schedule is made over the PA system, with announcement chimes signaling the final hour of the fair. Meanwhile, some students rehearse elevator pitches quietly against the wall, and others use tablets at kiosks to upload resumes to the fair database. Additionally, a startup founder invites students to a lunchtime pitch session, while workshops on networking etiquette begin in the adjoining classroom.

The engineering society sponsors a resume review table near the stage, and a whiteboard lists employers scheduling same-day interviews. Career center staff log attendance metrics on laptops, and announcement chimes signal the final hour of the fair. Concurrently, workshops on networking etiquette begin in the adjoining classroom.
